    note right of Unconnected
        bind() throws IOException if already bound.
        connect() transitions to Connected.
    end note

    note right of Connected
        getInputStream() requires Connected state.
        getOutputStream() requires Connected state.
        shutdownInput/Output() allows half-close.
    end note

    note right of Closed
        Terminal state. Cannot reconnect or rebind.
        setOption/getOption throw IOException if closed.
    end note
